Package com.github.yeetmanlord.zeta_core.sql

This is the SQL package.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISQL<SuperType extends ISQL<?>>
    ISQLs are SQL encodable objects.
    ISQLObjectHandler<SuperType extends ISQL<?>>
    Handler that loads and encodes SQL encodable objects.
    ISQLTable
    Represents and interacts with a specific SQL table
    ISQLTableHandler<PrimaryKeyType>
    This is a handler class for ISQLTable.
    ISQLTableHolder
    This is an ISQLTableHandler that isn't associated with a specific table but instead manages and controls multiple tables.

Package com.github.yeetmanlord.zeta_core.sql Description

This is the SQL package. It is a basic ORM for Zeta plugins. Maybe not a full ORM but enough of one that it gives me and you API developers a much better time since we don't have to deal with raw SQL!
Plugin Usage
Usable by other plugins
